Package model

package model
  • Class
    Description
    Bullet
    Bullet class is capable of representing a projectile.
    Coin
    Coin class is a game object that the player can touch to pick up.
    Collider
    The Collider allows for performing collision detection.
    Entity
    Entity is a universal game object that participates in an entity system.
    EntityEvent
    EntityEvent is a container for event classes.
    Explosion
    Explosion class represents an explosion in the game.
    Game
    The Main Game class.
    HealthBar
    HealthBar represents a health bar.
    House
    House represents an obstruction to the invaders (and even the player).
    Invader
    The Invader class is responsible for all Invader logic.
    InvaderCluster
    InvaderCluster contains Invaders to move and manage.
    InvaderGoal
    InvaderGoal only serves to be a line which seperates the invaders from the player.
    InvaderType
    InvaderType enum for invaders to keep track of what invader type/sprite they represent.
    Player
    Player class is responsible for allowing the player to interact with the game.
    Rect
    Rect types of Entity allow for representing an entity as a rectangle instead of just a point.
    Score
    The score class contains the current score of the game.
    Sprite
    Sprite is a rectangle entity that contains one or many images which it can cycle through and return when the rendering loop needs it.
    Team
    Representation of teams.
    Turret
    Turrets are objects similar to the player and invaders.
